all be a life of narrow scope and on the Day of Resurrection We shall raise him up blind.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2472.mp3","surahId":20,"words":[{"id":77069,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَنْ","translation":"আর যে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_124_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77070,"position":2,"arabic":"أَعْرَضَ","translation":"বিমুখ হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_124_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77071,"position":3,"arabic":"عَن","translation":"হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_124_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77072,"position":4,"arabic":"ذِكْرِى","translation":"আমার স্মরণ","audioUrl":"wbw/020_124_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77073,"position":5,"arabic":"فَإِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই তবে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_124_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77074,"position":6,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","translation":"তার জন্যে (হবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/020_124_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77075,"position":7,"arabic":"مَعِيشَةًۭ","translation":"জীবন যাপন","audioUrl":"wbw/020_124_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77076,"position":8,"arabic":"ضَنكًۭا","translation":"সংকুচিত","audioUrl":"wbw/020_124_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77077,"position":9,"arabic":"وَنَحْشُرُهُۥ","translation":"আর তাকে উঠাবো আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/020_124_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77078,"position":10,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","translation":"দিনে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_124_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77079,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْقِيَـٰمَةِ","translation":"ক্বিয়ামাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/020_124_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77080,"position":12,"arabic":"أَعْمَىٰ","translation":"অন্ধ অবস্থায়\"","audioUrl":"wbw/020_124_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77081,"position":13,"arabic":"١٢٤","translation":"(১২৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":125,"arabic":"قَالَ رَبِّ لِمَ حَشَرْتَنِىٓ أَعْمَىٰ وَقَدْ كُنتُ بَصِيرًۭا","translation":"[And so, on Resurrection Day, the sinner] will ask: \"O my Sustainer! Why hast Thou raised me up blind, whereas [on earth] I was endowed with sight?\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2473.mp3","surahId":20,"words":[{"id":77151,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_125_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77152,"position":2,"arabic":"رَبِّ","translation":"\"হে আমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/020_125_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77153,"position":3,"arabic":"لِمَ","translation":"কেন","audioUrl":"wbw/020_125_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77154,"position":4,"arabic":"حَشَرْتَنِىٓ","translation":"আমাকে আপনি উঠালেন","audioUrl":"wbw/020_125_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77155,"position":5,"arabic":"أَعْمَىٰ","translation":"অন্ধ অবস্থায়","audioUrl":"wbw/020_125_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77156,"position":6,"arabic":"وَقَدْ","translation":"অথচ নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/020_125_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77157,"position":7,"arabic":"كُنتُ","translation":"আমি ছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/020_125_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77158,"position":8,"arabic":"بَصِيرًۭا","translation":"চক্ষুষ্মান\"","audioUrl":"wbw/020_125_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":77159,"position":9,"arabic":"١٢٥","translation":"(১২৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]}]}